[ctns_make id='gen_axioms_axiom']

  [ctns_front style='']
Axiom
  [/ctns_front]  

  [ctns_back style='width:90%;font-size:80%;']
An <strong>axiom</strong> is a mathematical statement that serves as the starting point from which all other statements are logically derived. <br/><br/>An axiom can neither be derived by logic, nor demonstrated by mathematical proof.
  [/ctns_back]  

[/ctns_make]
